{
  "stem": "14463.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was watching it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Day and night, I was watching.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One day, I saw the-- the most-- the most the feasible thing is either to go by a little boat, or to go on the bridge.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But how do you do it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "On the-- on the bridge, they stand centuries.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They don't let you cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I saw one incident-- the-- the-- the Germans-- some Jewish people came down to the river bank, right?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they wanted to cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was a little boat in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So you want to cross?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Eh, no problem.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Cross.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put them all in, much more than the-- the boat could take.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They pushed them into the middle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He put a shot into the water and the whole thing sunk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, well, this is out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The next thing what I saw was that from the German side, there was a column of Red Cross trucks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Three or four trucks with the Red Cross on it, crossing the river, crossing the bridge.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were some people standing there in front, so the Germans started to scream [SPEAKING GERMAN] across, so that the column can go through.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, uh-huh, there's an idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was watching it, and watching it, and watching it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the meantime, there was bigger decrees, bigger decrees.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, you can't do that, and you can't do this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they said, if we catch you in the street, that-- that you don't belong in here, we'll forcibly [BACKGROUND NOISE] you know-- and then it will be-- we'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Will do this and that the other one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one day, I was sitting in there, and I saw a column from far away forming to cross the bridge.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
